SUMMARY:Shred It with AARP
LOCATION:2555 E. Hanna Ave Tampa \, FL 33545 United States
DESCRIPTION:Join AARP Florida and the City of Tampa for a free document sh
 redding event in Tampa Bay! Fight fraud by shredding your personal documen
 ts\, free of charge. This Shredding Event is for personal papers with a li
 mit of three bags or boxes per person. Business shredding will not be allo
 wed. Except for paper clips and staples\, no metal\, batteries\, electroni
 cs\, or other non-paper material can be in boxes or bags brought for shred
 ding. This event is free and open to the public. Register at AARP Florida 
